snippet.title: Drive Angry 3D: A Yay or Nay Review (starring Nicholas Cage and Amber Heard)
snippet.description:
Drive Angry 3D, stars Nicholas Cage as an escapee out of hell out to kick ass and kill a bunch of Satan worshippers. You want to know if you should see it, Yay or Nay reviewer Matthew Champ wants to tell you. 

PLUS - here are the full details for our March-long WIN WIN contest.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=24p6JGCA4dY

If you've seen the movie and agree with our review - or if you have a different opinion, tell us what you think in the comments below. 

Check out our Facebook page for exclusive content: 
http://www.facebook.com/yayornayreviews

Check out our other reviews at: youtube.com/shouldyouseeit

Yay or Nay Reviews
Produced by: Valley Wind Productions.
Reviewer: Matthew Champ
Producer: Allan Mackey
